@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = paste-admin-access-token-here

### Login and copy data.accessToken into @token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@finshield.ai",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### High-risk transfer; transactionReference is generated when omitted
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions/ingest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerNumber": "CUST1001",
  "sourceAccountNumber": "ACC1001",
  "destinationAccountNumber": "ACC9999",
  "beneficiaryName": "Unknown Beneficiary",
  "amount": 850000,
  "currency": "INR",
  "transactionType": "TRANSFER",
  "channel": "MOBILE_BANKING",
  "deviceId": "DEVICE-NEW-001",
  "ipAddress": "103.20.44.15",
  "geoLocation": "Unknown",
  "initiatedAt": "2026-06-22T20:00:00Z"
}

### Expected after asynchronous processing: HIGH and CREATE_ALERT
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
